color:#008CBA">sorymrz@yahoo.com</span></a><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify">
<span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify">
<strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Abogado Oscar Fernando Chinchilla</span></strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify">
<span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Fiscal General de la Rep&uacute;blica<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify">
<a href="mailto:fg@ministeriopublico.gob.hn"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#008CBA">fg@ministeriopublico.gob.hn</span></a><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify">
<span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
