<p style="text-align:justify">
<span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Subsecretar&iacute;a de Derechos Humanos Email:<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><a href="mailto:ygudiel@yahoo.com"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
color:#008CBA">ygudiel@yahoo.com</span></a><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
',
